weave and cloud66

Weave - the Docker network
Weave creates a virtual network that connects Docker containers deployed across multiple hosts.
http://weave.works/
https://github.com/zettio/weave#readme

10-15x cost savings moving from VM infra to cloud specially with containers
quick/speed, deploy more s/w automatically, capacity

Cloud66 - 
http://www.cloud66.com

Ops for Dev - basically you don't need dedicated ops manual teams for supporting development effort anymore - 
this can be done all in the cloud (Ops as a service) 
From building your servers to deploying your applications and managing your databases. 
All in one place.
